<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Mama Marketplace Account Activation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333333;
        }
        .email-wrapper {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .email-header {
            background-color: #ffa7b3;
            padding: 30px 24px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .email-body {
            padding: 30px 24px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }
        .email-footer {
            background-color: #f6f6f6;
            padding: 20px 24px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666666;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin: 0;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #ffa7b3;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        p {
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .activation-code {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            color: #ffa7b3;
            letter-spacing: 5px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #FFF5F8;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
       
        a {
            color: #ffa7b3;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="email-header">
            <h1>Welcome to Mama Marketplace</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <p>Hello <%= user.name %>,</p>
            <p>Thank you for joining Mama Marketplace! We're excited to have you as part of our community. To get started, please activate your account using the following code:</p>
            <div class="activation-code"><%= activationCode %></div>
            <p>Please enter this code on the activation page within the next 10 minutes to complete your registration.</p>
            <p>Once your account is activated, you'll have access to a wide range of products and services tailored for moms and families.</p>
          
            <p>If you didn't create an account with Mama Marketplace, please disregard this email.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team at <a href="mailto:support@mamamarketplace.com">support@mamamarketplace.com</a></p>
            <p>&copy; 2024 Mama Marketplace. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>